<title>USA: ITC completes purchase of Anderson.</title>
<headline>ITC completes purchase of Anderson.</headline>
<dateline>HERNDON, Va. 1997-01-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Industrial Training Corp (ITC) said on Friday it closed its acquisition of Anderson Soft-Teach, which develops, produces and distributes multimedia training solutions for computers and on-line electronic performance support systems.</p>
<p>ITC said it bought all outstanding stock of Anderson for a combination of $4.5 million and 300,000 shares of ITC stock.</p>
<p>The acquisition expanded ITC's distribution resources in the services market and its ability to provide just-in-time training solutions, the company. Anderson would be a wholly-owned subsidiary operating as Anderson Soft-Teach.</p>
<p>(( -- New York newsdesk 212-859-1610))</p>
